on diagrams for axial load and bending</span></span></span></p><p style="line-height:normal;"><span style="color:#515151;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">•Column design charts</span></span></span></p><p style="line-height:normal;"><span style="color:#515151;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">•Analysis and design of slender columns</span></span></span></p><p style="line-height:normal;"><span style="color:#515151;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">•The analysis and design of RC slabs</span></span></span></p><p style="line-height:normal;"><span style="color:#515151;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">•Conceptual behaviour of one-way and two way spanning slabs</span></span></span></p><p style="line-height:normal;"><span style="color:#515151;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">•Analysis and design of one-way slabs using beam model</span></span></span></p><p style="line-height:normal;"><span style="color:#515151;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">•Analysis of two-way slabs using yield line analysis</span></span></span></p><p style="line-height:normal;"><span style="color:#515151;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">•Analysis of punching shear</span></span></span></p><p style="line-height:normal;"><span style="color:#515151;"><span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;">•Design of reinforcement to resist punching shear</span></span></span></p></div>',
